---
title: Pork and Cheddar Burgers with Roasted Potato Wedges
description: Canadian-raised pork, gooey cheddar cheese and caramelized onions, what more could you want? An elegant side of roasted wedges served with a creamy chive dipping sauce makes for a match made in heaven!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-porc-et-de-cheddar-3c56e4bf.jpg
